race.description: The Women In Racing Luncheon 24th Oct Mdn Plate
race.comment: KING BLING (6) raced forward and boxed on to finish second over 1100m at this track last time. Should camp just off the leaders and won't know himself in Maiden grade. Fitter and tough to beat. DYNASTY REWARD (4) is returning from a spell and was last seen placing on the Ballarat Synthetic. Now with a new trainer Kevin Lamprecht and if presented on song can make his presence felt. APOLAKI (1) has also switched barns and was last seen 20 days ago over 900m at Mt Gambier. Race forward, and most of the extra gear comes off. In the finish at best. BATTLE JACK (2) tries had and is on a quick backup. Likely to be thereabouts.
